"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-23-andy-murray-retiring-olympic-tennis-tournament-paris-21254948\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Andy Murraydoesn't have long left in professional tennis before he officially enters retirement and hangs up his racket.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 120, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The British sporting legend, a two-timeWimbledonchampion and double Olympic gold medallist, is featuring on theParisclay at the Games thissummer.\", \"from\": 122, \"to\": 267, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 126, \"end\": 133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.908347066462221, \"rank\": 0.05389825487022023, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheOlympic tennis tournamentgets started on July 27 - and many fans want to know if it will indeed be Murray's final event before he calls time on his career.\", \"from\": 269, \"to\": 427, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 371, \"end\": 377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.345634456647623e-35, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's everything the former world No.1 and thee-time major winner has said so far about retiring, as the 37-year-old icon finally approaches the end of a remarkable career which was dramatically saved by a metal hip replacement.\", \"from\": 429, \"to\": 658, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Arrived in Paris for my last ever tennis tournament@OlympicsCompeting for \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00ac\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00a7 have been by far the most memorable weeks of my career and I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m extremely proud to get do it one final time!pic.twitter.com/keqnpvSEE1  On July 23, Andy Murray posted on X: 'Arrived in Paris for my last ever tennis tournament @Olympics competing for [Great Britain].\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 1010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 671, \"end\": 676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999849933, \"rank\": 1.4902678543149024e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 892, \"end\": 903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.442892702357007e-66, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 929, \"end\": 934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999849933, \"rank\": 1.4902678543149024e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 995, \"end\": 1008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_Davis_Cup_team\", \"score\": 0.9985652207100316, \"rank\": 0.0014367071726404123, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_Davis_Cup_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_Davis_Cup_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'[It has] been by far the most memorable weeks of my career and I am extremely proud to get do it one final time!'\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1126, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Two days later, Murraypulled out of the Olympic singlesand announced that he would only be playing in the men's doubles with Dan Evans.\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1263, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1253, \"end\": 1262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"score\": 0.8773522343202598, \"rank\": 0.13979307384434833, \"text\": \"Dan Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He then gave an interview to CNN and said: 'A couple of months ago, I definitely was unsure about when I wanted to finish or if I wanted to finish.\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1412, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1294, \"end\": 1297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"score\": 0.9999999999836291, \"rank\": 1.6482571576086447e-11, \"text\": \"CNN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was finding making that decision quite difficult and obviously consulted my family and my team.\", \"from\": 1413, \"to\": 1510, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'But ultimately, the decision had to come from me.\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1562, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But as I sit here today, I am really happy about it.\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1615, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am happy that I get to finish playing an Olympics with a lot of my\\u2026 I consider a lot of the tennis players on our team close friends of mine and getting to be around them and I have great memories from the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1833, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So, I am happy about it.'\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1859, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Andy Murraywas left in tearsas he spoke about his career on Centre Court after playing what is highly likely to be his last-ever match at Wimbledon in early July.\", \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 2023, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1921, \"end\": 1933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Centre_Court\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Centre Court\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Centre_Court\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Centre_Court\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It is hard, because I would love to keep playing but I can not,' Murray said about his upcoming retirement.\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2133, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2091, \"end\": 2097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.345634456647623e-35, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Physically it's just too tough now.\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2170, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All of the injuries have added up and like I said they have not been insignificant.\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2254, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I want to play forever.\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2280, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I love this sport.\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2299, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's given me so much, taught me loads of lessons over the years that I can use for the rest of my life.\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2404, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not want to stop so it is hard.'\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2442, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In hispost-match press conference, Murray appeared to leave the door open to continuing in doubles, only specifically ruling out singles when asked if he could be tempted to make a U-turn to play Wimbledon one last time next year in 2025.\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2682, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2479, \"end\": 2485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.345634456647623e-35, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Before what happened in Miami (a nasty ankle injury) I was starting to play good tennis,' Murray added.\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 2788, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2709, \"end\": 2714, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami\", \"score\": 0.9546739551585822, \"rank\": 0.04743189486462045, \"text\": \"Miami\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami\"}, {\"begin\": 2775, \"end\": 2781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.345634456647623e-35, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of all the memories Andy Murray has given us, one stands above the rest.On 7 July 2013, in living rooms and town squares across the country, we celebrated the end of a 77-year-wait\\u2026pic.twitter.com/j23kLcwkRE  'At Queens I got through the first round.\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 3040, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2810, \"end\": 2821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.442892702357007e-66, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can still win matches at this level.\", \"from\": 3041, \"to\": 3079, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even with the physical issues around the hip, I was still able to compete at the highest level.\", \"from\": 3080, \"to\": 3175, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Not as consistently as I would have liked.\", \"from\": 3177, \"to\": 3220, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Certainly not having the results I would have wanted.\", \"from\": 3221, \"to\": 3274, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'But yeah, I can definitely still win matches here or on the grass once I am recovered from the back injury.\", \"from\": 3276, \"to\": 3384, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I do not want to do that now.\", \"from\": 3385, \"to\": 3418, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know I could do it, but I have no plans to play singles again.'\", \"from\": 3419, \"to\": 3484, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking on June 27, Andy Murray said: 'I know that there is more important things in the world than how I finish playing my last tennis match or where I finished playing my last tennis match.\", \"from\": 3486, \"to\": 3678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3507, \"end\": 3518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.442892702357007e-66, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But because of what I put into the sport over the last however many years, I would at least like to go out playing a proper match where I am at least competitive, not what happened at Queen's (where his back injury forced a mid-match retirementand subsequent surgeryruled him out of Wimbledon singles).\", \"from\": 3680, \"to\": 3983, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'So I can not say for sure that if I wasn't able to play at Wimbledon, and I did not recover in time to play at the Olympics that I would not consider trying to play another tournament somewhere.\", \"from\": 3985, \"to\": 4180, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But if I am able to play at Wimbledon and if I am able to play at the Olympics, that's most likely going to be it.'\", \"from\": 4181, \"to\": 4296, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Andy Murray has said retiring at Wimbledon or the Paris Olympics would \\\"be fitting\\\" and he is unlikely to play at the US Open or Davis Cup later this year.He spoke to the BBC about his future planshttps://t.co/JJbKS1m5nlpic.twitter.com/NUKQLpdVca  Speaking to theBBCin June 2024, Andy Murray said: 'I do not think [I will play at the 2024 US Open or the Davis Cup].\", \"from\": 4298, \"to\": 4663, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4298, \"end\": 4309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.442892702357007e-66, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 4469, \"end\": 4472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999999782280613, \"rank\": 2.1770594578468244e-08, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 4578, \"end\": 4589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.442892702357007e-66, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Probably if I was going to finish my career I would rather finish at Wimbledon or an Olympic Games - to me that would probably be more fitting.\", \"from\": 4665, \"to\": 4809, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have had amazing experiences and memories from Wimbledon, but also being part of British Olympics teams.\", \"from\": 4811, \"to\": 4918, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4895, \"end\": 4902, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.908347066462221, \"rank\": 0.05389825487022023, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'To get a chance to compete at a fifth one is a reason to stay motivated and continue playing.'\", \"from\": 4920, \"to\": 5015, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking after he lost to Tomas Machac at the Miami Open in March, Andy Murray said: '[It is] the last match that I am going play here, which is sad, because I love it here.\", \"from\": 5017, \"to\": 5190, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5084, \"end\": 5095, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.442892702357007e-66, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have spent so much of my tennis career here and I would have liked it to have gone on a little bit longer.\", \"from\": 5191, \"to\": 5299, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'This tournament particularly for me is an important one so it was a bit more emotional leaving the court today than it might be at some of the other events.\", \"from\": 5301, \"to\": 5458, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am looking forward to the end now, give my best the next few months and get to be at home with my family.\", \"from\": 5459, \"to\": 5566, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Miami has been a special place for me during my career.\", \"from\": 5568, \"to\": 5624, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5569, \"end\": 5574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami\", \"score\": 0.9546739551585822, \"rank\": 0.04743189486462045, \"text\": \"Miami\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been my tennis home really.\", \"from\": 5625, \"to\": 5657, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have done so much of my work and training and preparation here.\", \"from\": 5658, \"to\": 5723, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I love the city.'\", \"from\": 5724, \"to\": 5741, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Yeah, I mean, I am likely not going to play past this summer,' Andy Murray said in February.\", \"from\": 5743, \"to\": 5836, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5807, \"end\": 5818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.442892702357007e-66, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I get asked about it after every single match that I play, every single tournament that I play.\", \"from\": 5838, \"to\": 5934, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am bored of the question, to be honest.\", \"from\": 5935, \"to\": 5976, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Yeah, I am not going to talk more about that between now and whenever the time comes for me to stop.\", \"from\": 5978, \"to\": 6079, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But yeah, I do not plan on playing much past this summer.'\", \"from\": 6080, \"to\": 6138, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking about his chances of featuring at the Games in Paris earlier this year, Andy Murray said: 'I would love the chance to play in another Olympics but also genuinely only if I felt like there was a chance of winning a medal.\", \"from\": 6140, \"to\": 6369, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6196, \"end\": 6201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999849933, \"rank\": 1.4902678543149024e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 6221, \"end\": 6232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.442892702357007e-66, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We have top doubles players and also Jack [Draper], Cam [Norrie] and Evo [Dan Evans] in singles as well.\", \"from\": 6371, \"to\": 6476, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6409, \"end\": 6413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\", \"score\": 0.6960013735540781, \"rank\": 0.4359985377665206, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\"}, {\"begin\": 6446, \"end\": 6455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"score\": 0.8773522343202598, \"rank\": 0.13979307384434833, \"text\": \"Dan Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not want to be in a position where I am getting selected to play there just because it might be the last tournament that I play.\", \"from\": 6477, \"to\": 6610, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'The [retirement] decision is my decision to be made, not anyone else's.\", \"from\": 6612, \"to\": 6684, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not see why there should be a keenness for people to stop doing what it is that they enjoy doing.'\", \"from\": 6685, \"to\": 6788, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After beatingDenis Shapovalovat the Dubai Tennis Championships in February, Andy Murray said: 'Look, I obviously still love competing.\", \"from\": 6790, \"to\": 6924, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6866, \"end\": 6877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.442892702357007e-66, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I still love the game but it's getting harder and harder the older you get, to compete with the young guys, keep your body fit and fresh.\", \"from\": 6926, \"to\": 7064, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Yeah, it is not easy.\", \"from\": 7066, \"to\": 7088, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I probably do not have too long left but I will do as best as I can these last few months.'\", \"from\": 7089, \"to\": 7180, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Andy Murraymouthed 'this game's not for me anymore'after losing to a player half his age in Qatar this year.\", \"from\": 7182, \"to\": 7290, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7274, \"end\": 7279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9931728796095516, \"rank\": 0.0068740488479856554, \"text\": \"Qatar\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was also forced to defend his legacy in the sport whena journalist accused the two-time Wimbledon champion oftarnishing his reputationwith poor results.\", \"from\": 7292, \"to\": 7447, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tarnishing my legacy?\", \"from\": 7449, \"to\": 7470, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do me a favour.\", \"from\": 7471, \"to\": 7486, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m in a terrible moment right now I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll give you that.\", \"from\": 7487, \"to\": 7545, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Most people would quit and give up in my situation right now.\", \"from\": 7546, \"to\": 7607, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m not most people and my mind works differently.\", \"from\": 7608, \"to\": 7664, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I won\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t quit.\", \"from\": 7665, \"to\": 7680, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I will keep fighting and working to produce the\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6https://t.co/nF0var6IfL  'Tarnishing my legacy?\", \"from\": 7681, \"to\": 7778, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do me a favour,' Murray said.\", \"from\": 7779, \"to\": 7808, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7796, \"end\": 7802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.345634456647623e-35, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am in a terrible moment right now I will give you that.\", \"from\": 7809, \"to\": 7867, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Most people would quit and give up in my situation right now.\", \"from\": 7868, \"to\": 7929, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I am not most people and my mind works differently.\", \"from\": 7930, \"to\": 7985, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I will not quit.\", \"from\": 7987, \"to\": 8004, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I will keep fighting and working to produce the performances I know I am capable of.\", \"from\": 8005, \"to\": 8089, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The only way to find solutions [is] to win matches.\", \"from\": 8090, \"to\": 8141, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It can also be played out in training, working on your game and sensations.\", \"from\": 8142, \"to\": 8217, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'At the moment, without a doubt, it is not easy to compete.\", \"from\": 8219, \"to\": 8278, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But what is happening now does not affect my career.\", \"from\": 8279, \"to\": 8331, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No number of defeats will change what I achieved when I was in shape and with two hips.\", \"from\": 8332, \"to\": 8419, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But when you can not win, you also lose confidence.\", \"from\": 8420, \"to\": 8471, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have never experienced that in my career.'\", \"from\": 8472, \"to\": 8516, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking after he lost in the first round of theAustralianOpen in January, Andy Murray said: 'It's definitely a possibility that is the last time I play here.\", \"from\": 8518, \"to\": 8676, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8593, \"end\": 8604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.442892702357007e-66, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have an idea when I would like to finish playing.\", \"from\": 8678, \"to\": 8730, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But so much of that depends on how you are playing.\", \"from\": 8731, \"to\": 8782, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'The time frame for that narrows when you play and have results like [that].\", \"from\": 8784, \"to\": 8860, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the nature of the performances that make you question things.'\", \"from\": 8861, \"to\": 8928, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking in the summer of 2023, Andy Murray said: 'I have heard stories from ex-players and other athletes who have made no plans for retiring, and they finish and all of a sudden, it's, 'What am I going to do with myself?'\", \"from\": 8930, \"to\": 9153, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8962, \"end\": 8973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.442892702357007e-66, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I was chatting to them about things that I might want to get involved in or really do not want to get involved in, just starting to get a few ideas together.\", \"from\": 9155, \"to\": 9313, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am looking for something I am really passionate about and that I want to work really hard at to achieve a specific goal.\", \"from\": 9314, \"to\": 9436, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'One area that ticks that box is coaching, but not necessarily in tennis.\", \"from\": 9438, \"to\": 9511, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I will definitely want to keep busy.'\", \"from\": 9512, \"to\": 9549, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray, in aMetro.co.ukexclusive interview in July 2024, was quizzed specifically if he wanted to enter tennis coaching and added: 'It's something that I will consider, for sure.\", \"from\": 9551, \"to\": 9729, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9551, \"end\": 9557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.345634456647623e-35, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have not made any plans yet past this summer.\", \"from\": 9730, \"to\": 9777, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Once I have finished my tennis, that's when I will start to think about what comes next.'\", \"from\": 9778, \"to\": 9867, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking to CNN later in July, Murray said: 'I am going to go home and I am going to spend time with my family and be around my kids.\", \"from\": 9869, \"to\": 10002, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9881, \"end\": 9884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"score\": 0.9999999999836291, \"rank\": 1.6482571576086447e-11, \"text\": \"CNN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\"}, {\"begin\": 9900, \"end\": 9906, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.345634456647623e-35, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have four young children which, I want to be at home for them and I want to avoid the long weeks of traveling and being away from that.\", \"from\": 10003, \"to\": 10140, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I found that hard the last few years.\", \"from\": 10141, \"to\": 10178, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I want to be home with them and take some time to relax and recover and have a think about what it is that I want to do, what it is that I want to do next.\", \"from\": 10180, \"to\": 10336, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I definitely still see myself having some involvement in tennis.\", \"from\": 10337, \"to\": 10401, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I am looking forward to something new now.\", \"from\": 10402, \"to\": 10448, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I am not entirely sure of what that new is yet.'\", \"from\": 10449, \"to\": 10501, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Team GB star claims Andy Murray has 'unfair advantage' at Paris Olympics  ArrowMORE:Why is not Emma Raducanu playing at the Olympics Games in Paris?\", \"from\": 10503, \"to\": 10661, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10533, \"end\": 10544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.442892702357007e-66, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 10608, \"en